'''Serowe''' ke motse mogolo wa morafe wa [[Bangwato]] o kgosi kgolo ya bone e leng Kgosi Seretse Khama Ian Khama.Bangwe ba bagaka ba morafe o ke Kgosi Bathoeng,Rre Seretse khama le ba bangwe fela jalo [http://www.en.wikipedia.org/Botswana Botswana].

Serowe o itsege thata fa ele motse mogolo mo Botswana morago ga motse mogolo wa Bakwena ebong Molepolole ebile ke one motse mogolo wa Bamangwato.Serowe o itsege thata ka ele one motse yoo bontsi jwa  botautona ba Botswana ba twang teng.

==Ditso==

Serowe o ntse o gakologelwa [[Khama III]],kgosi ya [[Bamangwato]]batho ba bogologolo ka ngwagakgolo lesome le boferabongwele masome mabedi.Ka ngwaga wa 1903 o ne a thomiwa fa e le motse mogolo  Serowe, Bamangwato.[[New International Encyclopedia]].Gape ke lefelo la matsalo a ga  [[Seretse Khama]],motswana wa ntlha [[President of Botswana|President]],le setso sa morafe wa letso la Bamangwato.

Sekolo sa Swaneng Hill e ne e le dingwe tsa dikolo tsa  ntlha mo Serowe tsa [[Brigades Movement]] dikolo di simolotswe ke morotegi [[Patrick van Rensburg]].

==Lefelo==
[[File:From Swaneng Hill, Botswana.jpg|left|thumb|View from Swaneng Hill east across the [[Kalahari]]]]

Serowe o bonwa mo lefelong le le siametseng temo thuo,lefelo le le tshwarang metsi mo Botswana [[Botswana Central District|Central District]] gape ke lefelo la kgwebo le thekiso.O bonwa mo bophirima jwa tsela ya [[Gaborone]]–[[Francistown]] kwa go leng motlhofo  teng go ka o bona.Gape le supa tshimologo ya tsela ya Serowe-Orapa  ee felelang ko meepong ya teemane ya Orapa.Tshimologo ya tsela e e simologile ka ngwaga wa 1986, mme e ne ya fetswa dingwaganyana morago.

Swaneng hill o kgaogantswe ka dintha di le tharo tse di bidiwang  Pa-Swaneng, Ma-Swaneng and Ba-Swaneng:Rre Mme le Ngwana ka go latelana.

==Dikago==
E sale ka ngwaga wa 2000, Serowe o nnile le dithabololo di le malwa,mme o tswelela ka go gola ka seemo se nametsang ntswa kgolo ya mabapi nae Palapye. Sekolo se se golwane sa Swaneng se se itsegeng ka leina la, swaneng hill,se ne gape sa thatosiwa maemo ke puso ya Botswana ka kompone ya tsa kago ya batho ba letso la chaina.Gompieno e na le felo la thathobelo ditsumpelo tsa segompieno tsa maranyane,le fa go ntse jalo ba thoka  ditsumpelo tsa kitso ee tseneletseng.Ka jalo ba nnile le kgatlhego mo maranyaneng,mme se se bakile gore ba romele bana ba ba nang le bokgoni ko ntle ga lefatshe.Go maleba go umaka fa ba na le kitso ya lephata la ditso ee kwa godimo ee isang bana go tsaya maeto a go ya difikantsweng go dikologa lefatshe.Dingangisanyo di rotuediwa thata, mme se se baka ditshimega di le malwa tsa lefatshe. 


